🌐 Landing Page

This is a basic landing page project built using **HTML** and **CSS**.  
It is fully responsive and designed as part of the ChaiCode Web Development Course on Udemy.

## 📂 Project Structure

landing-page/
├── index.html  
└── style.css  

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Clone the repository (if not already):

   git clone https://github.com/rachanadutta/Mini-Projects.git

2. Open the `landing-page` folder.

3. Double-click `index.html` to open it in your browser.

## 💡 Features

- Clean and responsive layout  
- Built with pure HTML and CSS (no frameworks or libraries)  
- Easy to customize and expand  

## 🛠️ Tech Used

- HTML5  
- CSS3  
